      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.12.2",
      "text": "A determination shall be made of the amount of openings in the building envelope for use in determining the enclosure classification. To make this determination, each building wall shall be assumed as the windward wall for consideration of the amount of openings present with respect to the remaining building envelope.",
